attributes.description: The "TYCHON Endpoint Browser" dashboard provides host visualization data for a single endpoint at a time. The dashboard is a set of several individual views broken down by tabs near the top of the screen. The TYCHON Endpoint Browser â€“ Software Inventory view displays all installed Applications and Products on a computer, its version, and the last time it was seen.
